| 10 | Anti-Forensics | Log clearing | `wevtutil.exe` — Security log cleared first |
| 11 | Impact | Backdoor account | `support` added to local Administrators |
| 12 | Lateral Movement | RDP pivot | `mstsc.exe` → `10.10.0.186` |

